title: Collab on YouTube!

embed.description: Check out my channel for some league of legend gameplays. :) If you love league, make sure u subscribe for new videos everyweek. :)) I also do RP giveaways, ...

body:
Hey guys, I have a YouTube Channel Yuci YZ. It's where I upload some of my games, and i also do a lot of RP giveaways.
But I've recently wanting to find someone to collab with on YouTube. If you have a gaming channel that plays League, and 
you wish to collab with me. Please let me know :) 
my email is yucizhang0218@gmail.com
Or even if you don't want to collab or you don't have a channel. You can always check mine out if you'd like to. :)
Hope you all have a nice day!
